    • rehash

      public void rehash()
      Expands table size when loadFactor exceeds LOAD_THRESHOLD post: the size of table is doubled and is an odd integer. Each non-deleted entry from the original table is reinserted into the expanded table. The value of numKeys is reset to the number of items actually inserted; numDeletes is reset to 0.
